1
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:09,770
How is it?

2
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,880
Based on the DNA comparison,

3
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:12,940
the victim is male.

4
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,039
Judging from the length of the arm,

5
00:01:15,039 --> 00:01:17,039
his height is between 175 and 185 cm.

6
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:17,450
Also,

7
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:20,200
the time of death is within the last three days.

8
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,520
Judging from the muscles on his arm,

9
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,770
he either worked out

10
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,880
or did manual labor.

11
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,120
Lao Jin,

12
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,760
the wrist of this arm

13
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,080
has a slight depression in the muscle.

14
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:35,610
Was this caused by being tied up before death?

15
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,560
I noticed that.

16
00:01:36,759 --> 00:01:37,759
It's not very obvious.

17
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:38,620
What caused it?

18
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,960
He probably wore a watch.

19
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:41,960
This mark

20
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,880
was caused after his death

21
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:45,120
by someone forcefully removing the watch.

22
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,880
A watch?

23
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:49,840
Brother Zhao.

24
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,060
Master.

25
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,600
I've checked with Missing Persons.

26
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,240
As for those who meet our age requirement,

27
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,300
there are only two.

28
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,600
What are their occupations?

29
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,930
One is a migrant worker,

30
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,600
and the other is a deliveryman.

31
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,440
Do you have the photos?

32
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,440
I sent them to you.

33
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,460
Anything else?

34
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,000
Go ahead.

35
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,930
I have work to do.

36
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:31,680
Chief.

37
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,120
You haven't gone home yet?

38
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,920
Can I?

39
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,160
Did you get the feeling back?

40
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,060
The feeling...

41
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,880
is very familiar.

42
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,560
Really?

43
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,360
I heard your cooperation

44
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,930
didn't go smoothly.

45
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,180
Well, it's not about being smooth or not.

46
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:51,000
Everyone has their own style of handling cases.

47
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,730
We just have different styles.

48
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:56,440
You even have a style now?

49
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,160
OK.

50
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,720
What's your style?

51
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,960
I want the case solved as soon as possible.

52
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,160
This case

53
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,720
is extremely vile.

54
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:13,520
The provincial department takes it very seriously

55
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,450
and has set up a special task force.

56
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:18,560
I don't care what problems you have in private.

57
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,800
The case must be solved.

58
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:22,930
Understood.

59
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,760
We are not familiar in private.

60
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:26,960
Exactly.

61
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,040
We must unite sincerely

62
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,740
and learn from each other.

63
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,280
Besides,

64
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,400
transferring you to the task force

65
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,880
was with your consent.

66
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,160
Yes.

67
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,020
There is no perfect crime.

68
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,320
There are only things

69
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,940
we haven't thought of.

70
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,440
Keep investigating.

71
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:47,170
Understood.

72
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:51,560
Don't talk to me about style anymore.

73
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,160
Rest assured, Chief.

74
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,520
Solving the case

75
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,060
is the only way.

76
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,600
Take care, Chief.

77
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,360
It's nothing.

78
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,920
What's wrong?

79
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,800
Are you upset?

80
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,399
No.

81
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,100
Don't be upset.

82
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:25,960
Go.

83
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:35,600
Hello.

84
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:36,960
Linlin.

85
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,050
When are you coming back today?

86
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,740
I won't be able to go back tonight.

87
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,210
I forgot my keys.

88
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,120
I can't go home.

89
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,960
I can't leave right now.

90
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:46,600
How about

91
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,000
you go back to your parents' place first?

92
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,360
I'll go to you to get them.

93
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,320
I'm too far away.

94
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,080
How about this?

95
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,360
I'll finish the discussion as soon as possible

96
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,560
and go back in a while.

97
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:56,800
Hello.

98
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,920
You haven't left yet, Captain Jiang.

99
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,320
You haven't left either.

100
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,400
I had a chat with the Chief.

101
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,930
What did you talk about?

102
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,890
He told me to cooperate with you fully.

103
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,280
Then listen to the Chief.

104
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,820
Tell me your thoughts.

105
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,620
We are on the same page.

106
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,760
Then we must have missed something.

107
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,540
Captain Jiang.

108
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:58,920
Can you lend me a few people tomorrow?

109
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,360
No.

110
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,700
But we can go together.

111
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,490
I'm leaving.

112
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,620
Captain Jiang.

113
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,500
Captain Jiang.

114
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,650
It's not that I don't trust you.

115
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,740
I just can't trust anyone.

116
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,720
Who asked you?

117
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:26,930
Goodbye.

118
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,770
I'm back. Where are you?

119
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,500
It's too cold outside.

120
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,250
I'm sleeping at a hotel.

121
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,420
I'll go pick you up.

122
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,320
No need.

123
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,620
I just feel bad for you.

124
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,720
You're so successful in your career,

125
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:54,020
but so subservient in your marriage.

126
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,240
What's the point

127
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,890
of living like this?

128
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,520
It's fine.

129
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,040
I have you.

130
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,050
With you in the company,

131
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,160
I feel reassured.

132
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,040
With you in my life,

133
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,400
I am happy.

134
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,120
What's wrong? Let me do it.

135
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:56,810
It won't kill me.

136
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,740
As everyone knows,

137
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,520
now is a critical period for the deputy mayoral election.

138
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:04,800
Xincheng definitely won't give up this opportunity.

139
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:07,320
If someone they are familiar with is elected,

140
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:09,760
it will be highly disadvantageous for us in the future.

141
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:12,440
Xincheng has been fighting with us for so many years.

142
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,760
As for the two projects in the city,

143
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,680
it has always been our two companies

144
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,920
splitting the market.

145
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:19,050
This is the best chance to devour them.

146
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,480
I will not give up this opportunity.

147
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,080
Besides,

148
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,700
I already have my own plan.

149
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,600
Next, the company will take a series of actions.

150
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,960
Yu Na will assist me in completing the rest of the plan.

151
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,600
However, I still ask everyone

152
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,860
for your full support.

153
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,560
Take him away.

154
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,720
I thought you weren't out of breath.

155
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,520
Captain Shen.

156
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,960
I'm not out of breath.

157
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:57,760
Then hand it over.

158
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,400
What?

159
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,400
You were swinging halfway up the mountain for so long.

160
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,460
It was hard to miss.

161
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:48,480
Hello, the number you dialed is powered off.

162
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,600
Hello.

163
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,490
How is it?

164
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,200
The fingerprints have been wiped clean.

165
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,460
There's nothing here.

166
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:12,200
Is their counter-investigation awareness really that strong?

167
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,000
Tell you what,

168
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,720
please check it thoroughly for us again.

169
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,200
If...

170
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:19,360
Everyone.

171
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,800
Let me give you an update.

172
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:22,680
As Captain Jiang ordered,

173
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:25,160
I pulled up the surveillance footage from all entrances and exits near Dahei Mountain,

174
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:25,840
brought them all up,

175
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,500
and reviewed them carefully.

176
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,480
I only saw some ordinary tourists

177
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,260
and didn't spot anyone carrying a large bag.

178
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:33,800
What about Zhao?

179
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,130
Any updates on your end?

180
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,760
I also checked the database.

181
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,560
I entered the victim's DNA,

182
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,720
but there was no match.

183
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,400
So right now,

184
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:44,400
the only valuable clue from the scene

185
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,800
is this watch that Captain Shen fished out.

186
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,010
Here's the plan.

187
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:57,880
We still need to strengthen the surveillance on Dahei Mountain.

188
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,400
We will continue our inquiries.

189
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,440
If there's any new information,

190
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,760
we will sync up immediately.

191
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:02,320
Okay.

192
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,400
Let's call it a day.

193
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:03,960
Good work.

194
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,440
Okay.

195
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,140
Can we talk in private?

196
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:17,840
Okay.

197
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,760
Excuse me.

198
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:19,360
Thank you.

199
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,240
Feng, just come in since you're here.

200
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:31,640
Look,

201
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:32,960
you're busy, so I won't bother you.

202
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:33,920
How have you been lately, Uncle Song?

203
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,050
Not bad, quite busy.

204
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:36,840
How about you?

205
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,810
Me? I'm back on the front lines.

206
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,320
Working on a case. I'm here on official business today.

207
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:43,580
Could you take a look at this watch for me?

208
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:49,490
This watch is a model from three or four years ago.

209
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:51,740
It was quite expensive back then.

210
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:53,360
It would cost you a year's salary.

211
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,290
That expensive?

212
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,680
I have a customer

213
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,140
who repaired this model here before.

214
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,360
I'll check later

215
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:02,280
to see which store in Tongjiang City

216
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,160
sold it.

217
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:04,600
Okay.

218
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,280
Let me know whenever you remember.

219
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:07,800
No problem.

220
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:08,360
I'll let you get back to work.

221
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,920
Your customers are waiting, so I won't bother you.

222
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:10,360
Thanks, Uncle Song.

223
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:10,920
Okay.

224
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:11,720
Keep in touch.

225
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:12,080
Thank you.

226
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:12,680
Come by if you need anything.

227
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:13,160
Okay.

228
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,000
Is this the entrance?

229
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,400
Yes.

230
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:53,480
Miss,

231
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,380
do you have a reservation?

232
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,480
I don't.

233
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,600
If you don't have a reservation,

234
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,560
please wait here.

235
00:13:58,560 --> 00:14:00,480
The customers ahead are waiting in line.

236
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:00,960
I see.

237
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:03,080
See what you'd like to drink.

238
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:05,700
Hey, handsome.

239
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:07,450
Can I ask you about someone?

240
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:09,600
Miss, who do you want to ask about?

241
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,800
This man.

242
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:12,360
He played with my feelings.

243
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,090
He didn't even tell me his name.

244
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,360
But I remember

245
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,360
he was wearing this watch.

246
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,500
Take a look.

247
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,120
We have too many customers here.

248
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,330
I didn't notice.

249
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,000
Take another close look.

250
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:28,480
Miss,

251
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,200
are you looking for someone?

252
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,640
I think I saw someone wearing it,

253
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,500
but I'm not sure

254
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:37,240
if he's the one you're looking for.

255
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:38,160
Do you want to see him?

256
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:38,560
Yes.

257
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:39,800
Then come with me.

258
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,880
I'll order drinks later.

259
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,080
Excuse me.

260
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,000
Excuse me.

261
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,200
Why did you drink so much?

262
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,120
Xiaoyun.

263
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:02,770
Take this

264
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,050
and enjoy it.

265
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,060
Why is there so much money?

266
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:08,880
Don't worry about it.

267
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:10,320
Just take it and enjoy.

268
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:13,800
How many rich people squander money like this?

269
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,400
I'm enjoying it,

270
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:17,610
not squandering it.

271
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:18,970
You've changed.

272
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:20,320
I've changed?

273
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,800
I went from broke to rich.

274
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,770
What's wrong with that?

275
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,640
What's wrong with you?

276
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:27,360
Let go of me.

277
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,920
Don't grab me.

278
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,840
What are you doing?

279
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,640
Who are you?

280
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,050
Are you okay?

281
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:43,890
I'm fine.

282
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,580
He's my boyfriend.

283
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,560
Stop messing around.

284
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:48,160
Got it.

285
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,640
Let him go home early.

286
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,400
Thank you.

287
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:10,000
Do you really know where he is?

288
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,720
Yes, I do.

289
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:12,120
It's just ahead.

290
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:12,960
Let's go.

291
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,050
Where exactly is it?

292
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:21,520
It's right ahead.

293
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,530
Just over there.

294
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:23,860
